dct_description_sm: Experimental product designed and prepared by U.S. Army Engineer Topographic Laboratories. (USAETL).
Aerial view map of Casablanca, Morocco showing railways, roads, buildings, wood land, power lines and grass and shrubs land.
Includes index to street, guide to numbered features, major commercial and industrial buildings and major places of interest.
"Experimental product designed and prepared by the U.S. army engineer topographic laboratories (USAETL), Ft. Belvoir, VA 6/72. Note: Base information has been supplemented with fictionalized data".
